  "description": {
    "zh": "老兄，欢迎回来！你说说，你觉得酒是个什么东西？我现在打算收集一些酒，但是我的伙计们到处翻遍了也找不到一滴酒。但是，你，长了个金手指，每次都能找到我需要的东西。总之，你愿不愿意帮我找点酒？事成之后我们畅饮一把！先从伏特加和威士忌开始吧。",
    "en": "Welcome, brother! Say, how do you feel about booze? I've got an order for a large batch of alcohol. Just imagine, there's war going around, but people still drink... Anyway, I need it to be fresh, so make sure you find only the good stuff. You've got golden hands, always find everything I need. So what do you think, can you find me some grog? We'll have a good drink to success after! Some vodka and whiskey would be great for a start. Oh, and get some water canisters too. For the eventual hangover, you know."
  },
